Package: wikifacts
Type: Package
Title: Generates messages with facts sourced from the Wikipedia main page
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Keith", "McNulty", email = "keith.mcnulty@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates messages containing random facts from the Wikipedia hompage.  
  Intended to keep users interested during long waiting periods.
